OL,3,CFundraising campaign to save Salford
OL,4,CLads Club gets #100k boost
OL,6,FA campaign to raise #250,000 to keep
OL,7,Fthe world famous Salford Lads Club
OL,8,Ffrom closure has been given a #100,000
OL,9,Fboost by the local authority.
OL,11,FSalford City Council said it will
OL,12,Fprovide the "significant funding" to
OL,13,Fhelp support the club, which offers
OL,14,Fsport and other activities six days a
OL,15,Fweek to more than 200 young people in
OL,16,Fone of the most deprived areas of the
OL,17,Fcountry.
OL,19,FThe cash will be donated with
OL,20,Fimmediate affect to help the club keep
OL,21,Fits doors open and remain operating.
