OL,3,CFundraising campaign to save Salford
OL,4,CLads Club gets #100k boost
OL,6,FSalford Lads Club, based on Coronation
OL,7,FStreet in Ordsall, has served as a
OL,8,Fcultural hub for decades, honing
OL,9,Ftalent from the world of art and sport.
OL,11,FThe 1960s pop group The Hollies used
OL,12,Fto practice in the club before they
OL,13,Fwere famous and earlier this week band
OL,14,Flegend Graham Nash made a #10,000
OL,15,Fdonation to save the Club.
OL,17,FIn 1985 the club was used as the
OL,18,Fsetting for an iconic image of
OL,19,FManchester band The Smiths.
