OL,3,CFundraising campaign to save Salford
OL,4,CLads Club gets #100k boost
OL,6,FThe image has brought the club global
OL,7,Frecognition and a source of funding
OL,8,Ffrom fans of the group. To this day
OL,9,Fthey make a pilgrimage to the building.
OL,11,FYoung footballers who trained there
OL,12,Fwent on to play for Manchester United
OL,13,Fand City as well as other top flight
OL,14,Fclubs.
OL,16,FArtist Harold Riley, who died last
OL,17,Fyear, was a member, as was radio DJ
OL,18,Fand member of the band Salford Jets,
OL,19,FMike Sweeney.
