OL,3,CFundraising campaign to save Salford
OL,4,CLads Club gets #100k boost
OL,6,FSalford City Mayor Paul Dennett said:
OL,7,F"I'm delighted to be able to confirm
OL,8,Fthis significant funding package for
OL,9,FSalford Lads Club.
OL,11,F"Having worked closely with the club
OL,12,Ffor many years, we are acutely aware
OL,13,Fof the current financial difficulties
OL,14,Fand the challenging operating times it
OL,15,Ffaces.
OL,17,F"So, I'm pleased we have been able to
OL,18,Fact swiftly and provide this funding
OL,19,Fsupport now."
