OL,3,CFundraising campaign to save Salford
OL,4,CLads Club gets #100k boost
OL,6,FThe club says costs have rocketed and
OL,7,Fit is finding it increasingly
OL,8,Fexpensive to maintain its 120 year-old
OL,9,FGrade II Listed home.
OL,11,FIncome from grants has slumped because
OL,12,Fthe market has become overloaded and
OL,13,Fcompetitive, bosses say.
OL,15,FThe club's annual utilities bill is
OL,16,F#15,000, building maintenance,
OL,17,F#15,000, and insurance costs #13,000.
