OL,3,CFundraising campaign to save Salford
OL,4,CLads Club gets #100k boost
OL,6,FIt needs #108,000 to cover the current
OL,7,Fmonthly losses for another six months
OL,8,Fwhile it gets initiatives established
OL,9,Fto generate more funds long term.
OL,11,FLast year the club's annual income was
OL,12,F#160,000. It included donations, money
OL,13,Ffrom open days and visitors, hiring
OL,14,Fout the building, including for
OL,15,Fweddings, and the online shop.
OL,17,FBut outgoings for the next 12 months
OL,18,Fare estimated at #394,700.
